creator: Psychic VR Lab Co., Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
STYLY for Nreal is a creative platform for XR artists of the next generation. Find yourself in the ultimate spatial experience created by artists of the new world. Free, no registration required.

■ “Art 3.0”
Experience XR artworks by cutting-edge talents from all around the world. Fashion, music, graphics -- all genres of art gather here. All artworks listed in STYLY are created with STYLY Studio, a free Web-based 3D creator tool for every artist, including yourself.

Lost in excitement? Start your journey with a step-by-step guide for beginners below:
https://styly.cc/manual/stylyfornreal-manual/

Webpage：https://styly.cc/
